Title: A Primalist Point of View
Description:
Warden Malathra has granted us permission to speak with the Primalists. They might have switched sides, but the wardens are keeping a close eye on them.
 
<Kelestra begins to look distressed.>
 
I'm going to talk to the Warden more. Could you handle the Primalists? All of this about Koroleth is just happening so suddenly. I feel we should gather as much information as we can.
ObjectivesText: Speak to the reformed Primalists about Koroleth.
